short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Explore the vast beauty of the universe with Galactic Harmony.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension transforms your new tab into a mesmerizing space journey, featuring a stunning arrangement of planets and celestial bodies against a cosmic backdrop. The vibrant colors and intricate planetary details create a captivating and serene atmosphere, inspiring wonder and exploration every time you open your browser. Bring the vastness of the galaxy to your screen and embark on a new adventure with every tab.
